# Beeceptor Login Credentials
# Create a free account at https://beeceptor.com and enter your credentials here.
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values.

BEECEPTOR_EMAIL=your-email@example.com
BEECEPTOR_PASSWORD=your-password

# Optional: Specify an existing endpoint to reuse to bypass rate limits
BEECEPTOR_ENDPOINT=your-existing-endpoint-name

